Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  今天请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.14,0:00:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.14,0:00:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有从经人那到剧本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.14,0:00:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有剧本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能写   不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.15,0:00:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要你抽1张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽到的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.16,0:00:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有写字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.17,0:00:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是指令的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.11,0:00:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要  要请你做那行为    我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来   请抽  真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.18,0:00:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个最轻松啊?   不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有轻松的   这张?   要抽那张吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.12,0:01:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要  我不会再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.20,0:01:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中间好了    可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.13,0:01:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张没问题吗   不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.21,0:01:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抽这张比较好?  可以吗?   那张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.14,0:01:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张?不知道.啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.21,0:01:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张  这张可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.16,0:01:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好   请看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.23,0:01:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸OO....身体在车内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.10,0:01:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊?是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样   可以退还吗?   ·不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.18,0:01:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要   那现在啊  就那写的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.12,0:02:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要请JULIA你来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.12,0:02:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧?  才不是没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.19,0:02:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下会说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗?今天不是没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请指教  虽不是没问题   但还是请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.21,0:02:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷摸摸惊心动魄性爱大作战JULIA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗?  我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说啊   那种的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸OO是身体在车内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.17,0:02:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  就是说啊  脸啊   OO什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO?现在某车站前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.18,0:03:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺多人经过的   能请你开窗户看一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗?    是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸稍微露出的状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来给JULIA你爽一下吧     是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会很可凝吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可疑吧?只要不出声就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.09,0:03:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉内裤吧    骗人?   对内裤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我脱掉吗?    真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?  真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.11,0:04:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吧?这样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是现在这状态话   脸也在车内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也在车内   不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出声会被发现珴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.22,0:05:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA    是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:06:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都湿了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.22,0:06:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么湿啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.17,0:06:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出?脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.16,0:07:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等    会被看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会看到胸部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?,    好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.19,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍住声音的话   可能会忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.13,0:07:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍住的话会被发现哦   那样不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.14,0:07:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为外面有很多人啊  会被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.28,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.14,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA小穴咕啾咕啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.08,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴咕啾咕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.09,0:10:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.09,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成啊   不讨厌这的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.10,0:10:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去时跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.20,0:11:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很湿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?快去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.17,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了    露出脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.21,0:13:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了好多汗   过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不关起来的话会被看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.16,0:13:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴咕咕啾啊    很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.24,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不需要裙子了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么关起来了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说已经以了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为已可以了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴真湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.23,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴整个撑开来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在忍耐吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又快去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.14,0:15:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'叫那么大声会被听见哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户已经关起来了   所以没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.15,0:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不露?出脸的话..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.22,0:16:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都会在车内啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会忍不住声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA好像......小穴的爱液流下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去了吗?躺下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.21,0:18:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.22,0:18:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.24,0:18:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再露脸了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那何以多叫点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.19,0:18:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.18,0:19:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在什么感觉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.18,0:19:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能叫出声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.12,0:19:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没侑被看到吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.19,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在忍耐   好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.27,0:20:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为会漏出叫声来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成不讨厌这种的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做之前是很讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.17,0:20:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了啊JULⅠA  到了啊  这里是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.19,0:21:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是那个啊  某 .....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.13,0:21:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是某......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA 这个 这张卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚JULIA   又抽了啊  这张卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.14,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.21,0:21:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那么真格的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.22,0:21:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请JULIA你做的也点过分  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就那个啊....去了再好好享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.16,0:21:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊?总之,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.23,0:21:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧.是  知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.16,0:21:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧  好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.24,0:21:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.17,0:21:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状态的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1日店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.18,0:22:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我行吗?  很好要看啊    要做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.19,0:22:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次来  好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.19,0:22:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊接下来这间点事JULIA的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.26,0:22:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  怎么办  那么多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.07,0:22:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有很多客人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.14,0:22:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人那.... JULIA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得啊    是来当店长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.15,0:22:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  想请你对店有贡献  要怎么做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.08,0:22:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是促进贩卖呢?这个如何的嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.22,0:22:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你去跑业务吗?   要怎做?我没跑过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.16,0:22:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道?  不知道    光是搭话的也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.16,0:22:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁?,那个人  欧吉桑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.17,0:22:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好   在找什么啊.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.24,0:22:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.18,0:23:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什么颜色啊? 果然  粉红色很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.25,0:23:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间店有很多种类啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.19,0:23:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有很多种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.26,0:23:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是粉红色好啊   是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.26,0:23:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多种类啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.20,0:23:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我'经常来啊   '请慢慢看  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.27,0:23:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒哦   好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害J.ULIA   怎么办?可以了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.15,0:23:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不再做一次?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.15,0:23:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,.....就那样去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.09,0:23:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,.....年轻人比较好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.23,0:23:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找什么?JüLIA?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.17,0:24:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.18,0:24:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 能握个手吗?   好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.25,0:24:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油   好，谢谢没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.25,0:24:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,.....请槾槾看好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.26,0:24:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到你很开心   谢谢，请槾慢看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.06,0:24:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是JULIA的粉丝吗?   一是的,
