Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:32.24,0:58:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说这种事....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:39.18,0:58:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘了   这要怎么办啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:43.18,0:58:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上去   要戴吗?
