Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:54.13,0:58:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长  不错啊 店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:59.20,0:59:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店有贡献吗？是啊  不过卖了2个自慰套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:04.14,0:59:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖了2个啊   还剩下1个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:07.21,0:59:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那....请男优买  男优...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:12.15,0:59:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一样的吗?是不是一样的,,,,,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:16.15,0:59:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那从酬劳  可以吗?从酬劳扣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:20.16,0:59:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,··不好意思 好贵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:24.16,0:59:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA你买的话会很便宜吧?请试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.10,0:59:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用原价买  原价?卖完了3个  太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:36.17,0:59:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  这已经有点.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:39.24,0:59:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了？  够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:44.18,0:59:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就去摄影棚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:48.18,0:59:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影棚  没有借
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:00.20,1:00:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视野真好啊  好棒
