Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.21,1:00:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那JULJA  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:23.15,1:00:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.22,1:00:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?因为是这种种规则啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.16,1:00:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抽了卡啊   我抽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:36.10,1:00:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个.....要全裸乳交
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.11,1:00:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这里..   会被看到哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.18,1:00:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不好吗?   这里不好啊  刚有人在看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.12,1:00:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？那....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.12,1:01:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大楼的  再更没人烟的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:03.19,1:01:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:06.13,1:01:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:11.20,1:01:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:17.21,1:01:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.22,1:01:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  我想不会有人来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:32.15,1:01:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有吧?    欸?大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:36.16,1:01:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果不是跟刚一样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:41.23,1:01:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可是  没问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.17,1:01:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:50.17,1:01:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会有人来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.18,1:01:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULIA也不讨厌紧张刺激的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:59.11,1:02:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有说过   可是那个和这个不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:06.19,1:02:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种虵方的不一样啊   不一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:09.26,1:02:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一样    知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.13,1:02:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啊....能请你脱衣服吗?
