Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:19.13,1:02:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会没东西遮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:22.20,1:02:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  会边把风边拍摄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:27.14,1:02:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗?外面不会有人来吗?
